    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"809\" data-end=\"835\">Rite of Caern Founding</strong><br data-start=\"835\" data-end=\"838\" /><em data-start=\"838\" data-end=\"872\">Caern Rite • Level 5 (Legendary)</em></p><p data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"1100\"><strong data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"883\">Time:</strong> Performed over time<br data-start=\"903\" data-end=\"906\" /><strong data-start=\"906\" data-end=\"915\">Cost:</strong> 100 Gnosis (may be contributed over time and shared by multiple Garou)<br data-start=\"986\" data-end=\"989\" /><strong data-start=\"989\" data-end=\"1005\">Requirement:</strong> A site of exceptional spiritual significance, completely free of Corruption and Wyrm influence</p><hr data-start=\"1102\" data-end=\"1105\" /><p data-start=\"1107\" data-end=\"1367\"><strong data-start=\"1107\" data-end=\"1122\">Description</strong><br data-start=\"1122\" data-end=\"1125\" />The Rite of Caern Founding is a legendary undertaking through which the Garou establish a new Rank 5 Caern. Unlike lesser Caerns, which grow through steady investment, this Rite represents a singular act of world-shaping spiritual commitment.</p><p data-start=\"1369\" data-end=\"1473\">This Rite is not performed in a single night.<br data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1417\" />It is completed when the land accepts the full offering.</p><hr data-start=\"1475\" data-end=\"1478\" /><p data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1617\"><strong data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1490\">Effect</strong><br data-start=\"1490\" data-end=\"1493\" />When a total of <strong data-start=\"1509\" data-end=\"1523\">100 Gnosis</strong> has been successfully invested at the chosen site, the location becomes a <strong data-start=\"1598\" data-end=\"1616\">Caern (Rank 5)</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"1619\" data-end=\"1645\">Gnosis may be contributed:</p><ul data-start=\"1646\" data-end=\"1817\"><li data-start=\"1646\" data-end=\"1668\"><p data-start=\"1648\" data-end=\"1668\">By one or more Garou</p></li><li data-start=\"1669\" data-end=\"1698\"><p data-start=\"1671\" data-end=\"1698\">Across multiple Caern Turns</p></li><li data-start=\"1699\" data-end=\"1749\"><p data-start=\"1701\" data-end=\"1749\">Gnosis invested is permanently bound to the site</p></li><li data-start=\"1750\" data-end=\"1817\"><p data-start=\"1752\" data-end=\"1817\">Partial investment has no effect until the full amount is reached</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1819\" data-end=\"1845\">Once completed, the Caern:</p><ul data-start=\"1846\" data-end=\"2023\"><li data-start=\"1846\" data-end=\"1876\"><p data-start=\"1848\" data-end=\"1876\">Begins with <strong data-start=\"1860\" data-end=\"1876\">Corruption 0</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1877\" data-end=\"1912\"><p data-start=\"1879\" data-end=\"1912\">Is immediately spiritually active</p></li><li data-start=\"1913\" data-end=\"1939\"><p data-start=\"1915\" data-end=\"1939\">May host all Caern Rites</p></li><li data-start=\"1940\" data-end=\"2023\"><p data-start=\"1942\" data-end=\"2023\">Enters the normal Caern upkeep and Corruption system starting the next Caern Turn</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"2025\" data-end=\"2028\" /><p data-start=\"2030\" data-end=\"2046\"><strong data-start=\"2030\" data-end=\"2046\">Restrictions</strong></p><ul data-start=\"2047\" data-end=\"2305\"><li data-start=\"2047\" data-end=\"2103\"><p data-start=\"2049\" data-end=\"2103\">The site must be free of Corruption and Wyrm influence</p></li><li data-start=\"2104\" data-end=\"2258\"><p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2152\">If Corruption is introduced before completion:</p><ul data-start=\"2155\" data-end=\"2258\"><li data-start=\"2155\" data-end=\"2179\"><p data-start=\"2157\" data-end=\"2179\">All progress is halted</p></li><li data-start=\"2182\" data-end=\"2201\"><p data-start=\"2184\" data-end=\"2201\">No Gnosis is lost</p></li><li data-start=\"2204\" data-end=\"2258\"><p data-start=\"2206\" data-end=\"2258\">The Rite cannot continue until Corruption is removed</p></li></ul></li><li data-start=\"2259\" data-end=\"2305\"><p data-start=\"2261\" data-end=\"2305\">This Rite cannot create Caerns of lower rank</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"2307\" data-end=\"2310\" /><p data-start=\"2312\" data-end=\"2527\"><strong data-start=\"2312\" data-end=\"2340\">Limits on Caern Creation</strong><br />A sept or Garou may only create one additional Rank 5 Caern beyond those already existing in the setting (ST discretion). This Rite is intended to be rare, political, and world-defining.</p><hr data-start=\"2529\" data-end=\"2532\" /><p data-start=\"2534\" data-end=\"2758\"><strong data-start=\"2534\" data-end=\"2576\">Interaction: Rite of the Opened Bridge</strong><br />Upon completion, the Garou may immediately perform the Rite of the Opened Bridge to connect the newly founded Caern to an existing Caern (all normal costs/requirements still apply).</p><blockquote data-start=\"2760\" data-end=\"2805\"><p data-start=\"2762\" data-end=\"2805\">“Some places are not grown. They are born.”</p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"2807\" data-end=\"2810\" /><p data-start=\"2812\" data-end=\"2945\"><strong data-start=\"2812\" data-end=\"2836\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"2836\" data-end=\"2839\" /><code data-start=\"2839\" data-end=\"2945\">[GAROU_RITE] type=caern; id=caern-founding; level=5; cadence=project; cost=100gnosis; requires=pure-site</code></p>",
      "chat": "<p><strong data-start=\"809\" data-end=\"835\">Rite of Caern Founding</strong><br data-start=\"835\" data-end=\"838\" /><em data-start=\"838\" data-end=\"872\">Caern Rite • Level 5 (Legendary)</em></p><p data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"1100\"><strong data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"883\">Time:</strong> Performed over time<br data-start=\"903\" data-end=\"906\" /><strong data-start=\"906\" data-end=\"915\">Cost:</strong> 100 Gnosis (may be contributed over time and shared by multiple Garou)<br data-start=\"986\" data-end=\"989\" /><strong data-start=\"989\" data-end=\"1005\">Requirement:</strong> A site of exceptional spiritual significance, completely free of Corruption and Wyrm influence</p><hr data-start=\"1102\" data-end=\"1105\" /><p data-start=\"1107\" data-end=\"1367\"><strong data-start=\"1107\" data-end=\"1122\">Description</strong><br data-start=\"1122\" data-end=\"1125\" />The Rite of Caern Founding is a legendary undertaking through which the Garou establish a new Rank 5 Caern. Unlike lesser Caerns, which grow through steady investment, this Rite represents a singular act of world-shaping spiritual commitment.</p><p data-start=\"1369\" data-end=\"1473\">This Rite is not performed in a single night.<br data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1417\" />It is completed when the land accepts the full offering.</p><hr data-start=\"1475\" data-end=\"1478\" /><p data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1617\"><strong data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1490\">Effect</strong><br data-start=\"1490\" data-end=\"1493\" />When a total of <strong data-start=\"1509\" data-end=\"1523\">100 Gnosis</strong> has been successfully invested at the chosen site, the location becomes a <strong data-start=\"1598\" data-end=\"1616\">Caern (Rank 5)</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"1619\" data-end=\"1645\">Gnosis may be contributed:</p><ul data-start=\"1646\" data-end=\"1817\"><li data-start=\"1646\" data-end=\"1668\"><p data-start=\"1648\" data-end=\"1668\">By one or more Garou</p></li><li data-start=\"1669\" data-end=\"1698\"><p data-start=\"1671\" data-end=\"1698\">Across multiple Caern Turns</p></li><li data-start=\"1699\" data-end=\"1749\"><p data-start=\"1701\" data-end=\"1749\">Gnosis invested is permanently bound to the site</p></li><li data-start=\"1750\" data-end=\"1817\"><p data-start=\"1752\" data-end=\"1817\">Partial investment has no effect until the full amount is reached</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1819\" data-end=\"1845\">Once completed, the Caern:</p><ul data-start=\"1846\" data-end=\"2023\"><li data-start=\"1846\" data-end=\"1876\"><p data-start=\"1848\" data-end=\"1876\">Begins with <strong data-start=\"1860\" data-end=\"1876\">Corruption 0</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1877\" data-end=\"1912\"><p data-start=\"1879\" data-end=\"1912\">Is immediately spiritually active</p></li><li data-start=\"1913\" data-end=\"1939\"><p data-start=\"1915\" data-end=\"1939\">May host all Caern Rites</p></li><li data-start=\"1940\" data-end=\"2023\"><p data-start=\"1942\" data-end=\"2023\">Enters the normal Caern upkeep and Corruption system starting the next Caern Turn</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"2025\" data-end=\"2028\" /><p data-start=\"2030\" data-end=\"2046\"><strong data-start=\"2030\" data-end=\"2046\">Restrictions</strong></p><ul data-start=\"2047\" data-end=\"2305\"><li data-start=\"2047\" data-end=\"2103\"><p data-start=\"2049\" data-end=\"2103\">The site must be free of Corruption and Wyrm influence</p></li><li data-start=\"2104\" data-end=\"2258\"><p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2152\">If Corruption is introduced before completion:</p><ul data-start=\"2155\" data-end=\"2258\"><li data-start=\"2155\" data-end=\"2179\"><p data-start=\"2157\" data-end=\"2179\">All progress is halted</p></li><li data-start=\"2182\" data-end=\"2201\"><p data-start=\"2184\" data-end=\"2201\">No Gnosis is lost</p></li><li data-start=\"2204\" data-end=\"2258\"><p data-start=\"2206\" data-end=\"2258\">The Rite cannot continue until Corruption is removed</p></li></ul></li><li data-start=\"2259\" data-end=\"2305\"><p data-start=\"2261\" data-end=\"2305\">This Rite cannot create Caerns of lower rank</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"2307\" data-end=\"2310\" /><p data-start=\"2312\" data-end=\"2527\"><strong data-start=\"2312\" data-end=\"2340\">Limits on Caern Creation</strong><br />A sept or Garou may only create one additional Rank 5 Caern beyond those already existing in the setting (ST discretion). This Rite is intended to be rare, political, and world-defining.</p><hr data-start=\"2529\" data-end=\"2532\" /><p data-start=\"2534\" data-end=\"2758\"><strong data-start=\"2534\" data-end=\"2576\">Interaction: Rite of the Opened Bridge</strong><br />Upon completion, the Garou may immediately perform the Rite of the Opened Bridge to connect the newly founded Caern to an existing Caern (all normal costs/requirements still apply).</p><blockquote data-start=\"2760\" data-end=\"2805\"><p data-start=\"2762\" data-end=\"2805\">“Some places are not grown. They are born.”</p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"2807\" data-end=\"2810\" /><p data-start=\"2812\" data-end=\"2945\"><strong data-start=\"2812\" data-end=\"2836\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"2836\" data-end=\"2839\" /><code data-start=\"2839\" data-end=\"2945\">[GAROU_RITE] type=caern; id=caern-founding; level=5; cadence=project; cost=100gnosis; requires=pure-site</code></p>"
